            <h2>Be Prepared to Speak With an Advisor</h2>
            <p>
                Your advisor (academic or faculty) will have the opportunity to give you more valuable information if you come prepared. When you come in, please have the following documents with you:
           <ul>
               <li><strong>Class Schedule:</strong> courses you are currently registered for
               </li>
               <li><strong>Unofficial Transcript:</strong> for all colleges attended&nbsp;
               </li>
               <li><a title="Program Requirement Sheet" href="http://catalog.edcc.edu/content.php?catoid=48&amp;navoid=13964" target="_blank"><strong>Program Requirement Sheet</strong>:</a> filled in with courses you have completed towards your degree/certificate
               </li>
               <li><strong>Official Credit Evaluation:</strong> if one has been done
               </li>
               <li>Any <strong>academic/career planning</strong> you have done
               </li>
           </ul>
            </p>
